## Downloads

Downloads module is available for Regular product mode.

This module can be used to securely deliver files for different use cases:

1. **Sell assets:** Assets are automatically shared with customer upon order approval
2. **Sell digital services:** Assets are manually shared with customer after order is approved and service is fulfilled by the seller.

After enabling the module, you can configure it on the Downloads tab.

Settings include:

- Delivery method
- File size and count
- File formats

![](data:image/png;base64,)

When Automatic mode is enabled, the files are uploaded during post submission

![](data:image/png;base64,)

Then shared once the order is approved

![](data:image/png;base64,)

In the other hand, when Manual delivery is enabled, the vendor can upload files manually after order approval

![](data:image/png;base64,)
